{"tid":1558733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「有巴打已寫好，歡迎轉載」紀念911 暫停示威活動","createTime":"2019-09-10T14:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T18:01:28.000Z","uid":33307,"like":113,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"4c9f4b6dd12d3b0a68635e4a7218f8680ece38c5","tid":1558733,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:29:01.000Z","msg":"Suspension of Protest in Remembrance of the September 11 Attacks<br />\n<br />\nIn remembrance of the September 11 attacks, and in solidarity against terrorism, all forms of protest in Hong Kong will be suspended on 11 Sept (HKT) apart from potential singing and chanting. We honour those who died in the attacks, and all those sacrificed in the fight against all forms of terrorism. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紀念911 暫停示威活動<br />\n<br />\n為紀念911及團結對抗恐襲，除唱誦口號及歌曲外，所有示威活動將會於香港時間9月11日暫停一天。我們向死難者及所有對抗恐襲之殉難者致以敬意。"},{"pid":"2e18f82e5f37b4efb1d8cd248ce09ba5d56dafe2","tid":1558733,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:30:04.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫手推"},{"pid":"cec9b9923b597ea3fc8c836b4ef66e476c0beff7","tid":1558733,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:30:53.000Z","msg":"中英對照，人人睇得明"},{"pid":"c93a8136b7d67f4d60d57a1c9d15c8fb68dce1eb","tid":1558733,"uid":186845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fac1d07fbd41f2ba1e4d1e5878b9dcdb061e560","tid":1558733,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"一人一推"},{"pid":"bcc2bcf1be64e3bcf9a286cce8dec2c396cf8801","tid":1558733,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:31:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1862e1c09c3665f4d765bbc3b73be437fd170424","tid":1558733,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bdb1dfdb31e470e62dd5fc65c9df77605c75c94","tid":1558733,"uid":318195,"